decks.notes: The main focus of this deck is to control the game through counterspells and removal spells, utilizing cards like Force of Will, Swords to Plowshares, and Teferi, Time Raveler to disrupt the opponent's game plan. The deck also includes cards like Back to Basics and Magus of the Moon to further hinder the opponent's mana development. With card draw spells like Ponder and Brainstorm, the deck aims to keep the hand full and consistently have answers to threats. Tamiyo, Inquisitive Student and Thundertrap Trainer provide additional card advantage and utility options.
